  - guid: ed4a66d8-7c7d-434c-9f2d-784eacc94d69
    nodeType: 1
    position: {x: 780, y: 165}
    speakerName: Alexander
    dialogueText: "You really love it, don\u2019t you? Alright here goes."
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 216b1a5d8087ae64bb513f600ffeba03, type: 3}
    sceneryId: 
    choices: []
    conditionVariable: 
    conditionValue: 
    conditionType: 0
    conditionPorts: []
    actionVariable: 
    actionValue: 
    actionType: 0
    variableName: 
    compareValue: 
  - guid: 858e01a3-e37f-4d3b-8e6d-8101acd76a1e
    nodeType: 1
    position: {x: 1262, y: 161}
    speakerName: Alexander
    dialogueText: Once upon a time a girl just like you was going home after a long
      day outside. The girl found a wounded squirrel and without hesitation took
      it home to tend to its wounds.
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 216b1a5d8087ae64bb513f600ffeba03, type: 3}
    sceneryId: 
    choices: []
    conditionVariable: 
    conditionValue: 
    conditionType: 0
    conditionPorts: []
    actionVariable: 
    actionValue: 
    actionType: 0
    variableName: 
    compareValue: 
  - guid: e4e341ab-5771-4175-8a05-6c07c0d0f170
    nodeType: 1
    position: {x: 2354, y: 165}
    speakerName: Alexander
    dialogueText: The squirrel became eternally grateful, and used magic to bless
      the girl. Ever so kind, the girl used her blessing to help the people of her
      village.
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 216b1a5d8087ae64bb513f600ffeba03, type: 3}
    sceneryId: 
    choices: []
    conditionVariable: 
    conditionValue: 
    conditionType: 0
    conditionPorts: []
    actionVariable: 
    actionValue: 
    actionType: 0
    variableName: 
    compareValue: 
  - guid: e8fe251d-03a3-402d-bc8f-78fdaab13948
    nodeType: 1
    position: {x: 3328, y: 169}
    speakerName: Alexander
    dialogueText: "The villagers, amazed by the girl\u2019s many capabilities, hailed
      her as a goddess and hailed her as a being beyond the stars."
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 216b1a5d8087ae64bb513f600ffeba03, type: 3}
    sceneryId: 
    choices: []
    conditionVariable: 
    conditionValue: 
    conditionType: 0
    conditionPorts: []
    actionVariable: 
    actionValue: 
    actionType: 0
    variableName: 
    compareValue: 
  - guid: 6b3ed655-7e20-4d87-92a6-741159f7ad18
    nodeType: 1
    position: {x: 4315, y: 168}
    speakerName: Alexander
    dialogueText: "That however, angered a god, who looked upon the many people worshiping
      something it considered \u201Cinferior\u201D. It cursed the lands below, causing
      devilish creatures to sprang from the ground and began terrorizing the once
      peaceful villagers."
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1202499a100b7d047b9b6fee39a9e5b3, type: 3}
    sceneryId: 
    choices: []
    conditionVariable: 
    conditionValue: 
    conditionType: 0
    conditionPorts: []
    actionVariable: 
    actionValue: 
    actionType: 0
    variableName: 
    compareValue: 
  - guid: e12151be-df46-4500-9dcf-fc696f4888f8
    nodeType: 1
    position: {x: 5807, y: 167}
    speakerName: Alexander
    dialogueText: The girl jumped in front of the villains, but only her blood was
      spilled in return. The blessings of her kindness slowly dripped out of her
      dying body, and graced the land.
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1202499a100b7d047b9b6fee39a9e5b3, type: 3}
    sceneryId: 
    choices: []
    conditionVariable: 
    conditionValue: 
    conditionType: 0
    conditionPorts: []
    actionVariable: 
    actionValue: 
    actionType: 0
    variableName: 
    compareValue: 
  - guid: e949004c-32ec-41dd-9ce4-abd3b6f2a686
    nodeType: 1
    position: {x: 6918, y: 161}
    speakerName: Alexander
    dialogueText: And from this land, creatures known as the Celestia were born,
      and those who were chosen by the celestia became Luminary, protectors of peace.
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 216b1a5d8087ae64bb513f600ffeba03, type: 3}
    sceneryId: 
    choices: []
    conditionVariable: 
    conditionValue: 
    conditionType: 0
    conditionPorts: []
    actionVariable: 
    actionValue: 
    actionType: 0
    variableName: 
    compareValue: 
  - guid: b5401c5d-752d-4600-8dd0-a1c32acfbb46
    nodeType: 1
    position: {x: 8492, y: 157}
    speakerName: Alexander
    dialogueText: Of course, I'm more than sure a Celestia will take a liking to
      you.
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 216b1a5d8087ae64bb513f600ffeba03, type: 3}
    sceneryId: 
    choices: []
    conditionVariable: 
    conditionValue: 
